Senior IT Operation Specialist – Server  -
Senior IT Operation Specialist – Server
Responsibilities
Mainly responsible for IT Operation support and to ensure that all IT services can operate smoothly and effectively 24 hours 7 days with high reliability and meet committed Service Level Agreement (SLA). It also includes managing Network system for the company by minimizing downtime to support non-stop business operation. Requirements: Education : Bachelor Degree in Computer Science, or Computer Engineering, or Electrical Engineering or other computer and telecommunication system related field Experience : Minimum 5 years experience in IT Operation Support (PC, Notebook, Server, Network and etc.)Computer literacy : SAP, Microsoft Office, Windows Language : Good command in English both oral & written Other qualification / skills : Proficient with Computer & its related technologiesGood in Analysing & Problem Solving SkillDetail-minded individualGood interpersonal SkillAbility to communicate effectivelyTime management and reportingGood Leadership & Coaching SkillTeam PlayerGood PBX/voice technical skillWilling to work fast under pressureFlexibility to adapt and adopt changes If you are are interested to the position, please send your resume to:Organizational Development Dept.recruitment-idn@holcim.com(Please indicate the position applied for on the subject field of your email)
